{"tid":1475930,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「大新聞」警元朗檢7汽油彈，拘三人包括兩名內地男","createTime":"2019-08-15T15:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T17:07:19.000Z","uid":230104,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"267e4d337b87b551f361bf2625353cb5ffc6ee00","tid":1475930,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:46:10.000Z","msg":"警方今早在巡邏期間，發現一輛私家車停泊在元朗青山公路屏山段往天水圍方向路邊，形迹可疑，遂上前截查。3名站在私家車旁的男子隨即往元朗方向逃去，另一名男子則駕駛私家車向屯門方向逃去，警員隨即上前追截。另一批警員在一個由私家車掉落的紙箱內，檢獲7個懷疑氣油彈。3名逃跑的男子涉嫌藏有工具可作非法用途被捕，包括一名35歲李姓內地男子、61歲程姓男子及26歲李姓內地男子。案件交由元朗警區刑事調查隊第十二隊跟進，並正追緝駕車離開的男子。35歲李姓內地男子逃走期間意外受傷，報稱手痛，清醒被送博愛醫院治理。"},{"pid":"91bc9ed98bc7e62b24268505a63dc0b27b22093d","tid":1475930,"uid":230104,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:46:57.000Z","msg":"準備扮示威者818混入人群"},{"pid":"f03153f764586a73ff5887db6fc5d2aa32ceb579","tid":1475930,"uid":108606,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:47:05.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒！<br />\n自己人嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1130c4d4554fcaf39cd37c0e9038273b4f31f44b","tid":1475930,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:47:29.000Z","msg":"補source<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190815/s00001/1565881331334/%E8%AD%A6%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%AA%A27%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%85%A9%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190815%2Fs00001%2F1565881331334%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%25AA%25A27%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%258B%2598%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%258B%25AC%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25B7&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg426uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=b8ba6d5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F